comments: Butler (MIA) establishes himself in Bryant's (LAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Adebayo (MIA) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Oladipo (MIA) gathers the ball on his right foot and comes to a jump stop on two feet, prior to releasing his jump shot attempt.

Adebayo (MIA) reaches in and makes contact with the ball that dislodges it away from Schroder (LAL) during his driving shot attempt. The contact to Schroder's arm after the ball is dislodged, is deemed incidental.
Butler (MIA) legally contests Westbrook's (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Westbrook (LAL) briefly places a hand on Butler's (MIA) lower body and marginal contact occurs during the jump shot attempt.
Oladipo (MIA) initiates contact with Schroder's (LAL) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Replay review of the foul called on Reaves (LAL)  pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful and the call on the floor would stand as a blocking foul on Reaves.
Toscano-Anderson (LAL) is moving alongside Butler's (MIA) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Toscano-Anderson (LAL) moves alongside Butler's (MIA) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Westbrook (LAL) makes marginal contact to Adebayo's (MIA) body that does not affect his put-back near rim.
Oladipo (MIA) initiates contact with Westbrook's (LAL) head during the layup attempt.
Lowry (MIA) commits a take foul on Schroder (LAL).
Toscano-Anderson (LAL) legally contests Butler's (MIA) jump shot attempt.
